```
rsync -a --include=*.tiff --info=progress2 systems@imagecat2:/var/www/html/imagecat/disk2 /tmp/disk2
```

tmux:
```
tmux new -s transfer
```
to exit tmux Ctrl-b d
to list tmux sessions
```
tmux ls
```
to attach 
```
tmux attach
```
